# Implementation Plan - Light Mode & Aesthetic Overhaul

The goal is to strictly enforce light mode and significantly improve the application's visual aesthetics to be "premium" and "rich", avoiding generic looks.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This change will PERMANENTLY remove Dark Mode support. The app will be Light Mode only.

## Proposed Changes

### Theme & Colors
#### [MODIFY] [app_colors.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/theme/app_colors.dart)
- Remove `isDark` toggle (or force false).
- meaningful update to the Light Color Palette:
    - **Background**: `0xFFFAFAFA` (Clean Off-White) -> `0xFFFDFCF8` (Warm Premium Paper)
    - **Surface**: `0xFFFFFFFF` (White) -> `0xFFFFFFFF` (Pure White with shadow) or `0xFFFFF0F5` (Very subtle rose tint if applicable)
    - **Primary**: Refine rose color to be more elegant.
    - **Typography**: Ensure high contrast but softer than pure black (`0xFF2D2D35`).

### Main Entry Point
#### [MODIFY] [main.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart)
- Remove [toggleTheme](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/main.dart#43-48).
- Set `themeMode: ThemeMode.light`.
- Update `ThemeData` to use the new [AppColors](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/theme/app_colors.dart#3-25).

### Components
